    <string name="app_description">
        Objective is to find all diamonds! Tap on a tile to scan for diamonds at its row/column.
        Tap another time on a diamond you found for another scan (it will increase your total scans).
        You can also choose grid size and number of mines in the options page. Have fun!
    </string>

